Who am I?

I have been a front-end engineer at Yahoo for the past two years. Working at Yahoo! Tech, then Yahoo! Mail, and now Yahoo! Music. Before that I spent more then 10 years hacking on a variety of personal projects.

My profesional, as well as pearsonal mission, is too never stop learning, and I always work with an intention of getting better at what I do. Even when working on one-off projects, learning, or trying something new is important to me.

I am always on the look out for a fun new project to try, that will teach me something.
